<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333333; /* Default text color */
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      border-top-left-radius: 10px;
      border-top-right-radius: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 30px;
    }
    .content h1, .content p {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333333; /* Ensuring consistent text color */
    }
    .content h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 30px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background-color: #af0000;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #991212;
    }
    .social-icons {
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .social-icons a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }
    .social-icons img {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .content h1 {
        font-size: 22px;
      }
      .content p {
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .btn {
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://static.scientificamerican.com/sciam/cache/file/952E6352-90DE-47D9-ABC8E1C464ADF6FB_source.jpg?w=900" alt="Banner">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h1 style="color: #333333;">{{name}}, Tu esi pacēlies!</h1>
      <p style="color: #333333;">Apsveicu, ar veiksmīgu startu, bet nu ir laiks šauties uz preikšu!</p>
      <p style="color: #333333;">Ceļā no bāzes raķete nekad neapstājas, nekad nesabremzējas un tikai tāpēc misija ir veiksmīga.</p>
      <p style="color: #333333;">Tava treniņprogramma ir trajektorija ceļā uz mērķi.</p>
      <p style="color: #333333;">Vienīgais kurš šai misijai var likt izdoties esi Tu un tikai Tevis dēļ misija var izgāsties!</p>
      <p style="color: #333333;">TAVA IZVĒLE</p>
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1oMrSgnYp54GaVxjGBW4_7Q3EmmVBs1GFg_k99bb8Y-E/edit?usp=sharing" class="btn" style="color: white; text-decoration: none;">Muskuļu masas palielināšanas treniņprogramma</a>
      <p style="color: #333333;">Trajektorijas precizēšanai apskati manu profilus.</p>
      <div class="social-icons">
        <a href="https://discord.gg/3QfjkETaSk" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
          <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2111/2111370.png" alt="Discord">
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@mikelis_silins" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
          <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1384/1384060.png" alt="YouTube">
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/mikelis_silins/" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
          <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733558.png" alt="Instagram">
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p style="color: #777;">"Laiks izšauties cauri Atmosfērai"<br>- Miķelis Siliņš -</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
